data.description:
Welcome Home! Three full bedrooms plus a den and 2 full baths - open floor plan home with ceramic wood plank tile floors and plantation shutters will WOW  you upon entering. Spacious kitchen with ample cabinets and granite tops is ideal for family gatherings. 
This homes desirable location with quick easy access to shopping, Goodyear ballpark and Community Center makes it a win win on the west side!
No need to fret the mechanicals - they've all been updated too!  HVAC 15seer(20), WaterHeater(20), WaterSoftener(18), RO (18), GarageDoor(18), ExteriorPaint (23) and new main water line (17)
